snippet.title: E3 2010 Konami - Otomedius Excellent (overview and trailer)
snippet.description: A brief overview of Otomedius Excellent, the newest title of the Otomedius series, explaining the gameplay and features. Go to 1:58 for the fanservice trailer (no gameplay in it).
